ge between <i>Edmund</i> and <i>Edward</i>."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Edmund Robyns I was born about 1495, in Whichford, Warwickshire, England, United Kingdom, his father, John Robyns II, was 27 and his mother, Johanna, was 23. He married Abigail Worton in 1530, in Stourton, Warwickshire, England. They were the parents of at least 2 sons. He died about 1532, in Harrowden, Northamptonshire, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 39."},"et":{"Abt 1495–Abt 1532":"umbes 1495–umbes 1532","1495–1532":"1495–1532","1500–1560":"1500–1560","1499–1550":"1499–1550","1515–1575":"1515–1575","1532–1627":"1532–1627","1469–1544":"1469–1544","1473–1560":"1473–1560","1473":"1473","1550":"1550","1495":"1495","1494":"1494","1560":"1560","Abt 1532":"umbes 1532","1469":"1469","1544":"1544","1500":"1500","1532":"1532","1499":"1499","1575":"1575","1530":"1530","Abt 1495":"umbes 1495","1627":"1627","1515":"1515","Stourton, Warwickshire, England":"Stourton, Warwickshire, England","Kent, England":"Kent, England","Whichford, Warwickshire, England":"Whichford, Warwickshire, England","Harrowden, Northamptonshire, England":"Harrowden, Northamptonshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Stourton, Stratford-on-Avon, Warwickshire, England, United Kingdom":"Stourton, Warwickshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1495–Abt 1532":"noin 1495–noin 1532","1495–1532":"1495–1532","1500–1560":"1500–1560","1499–1550":"1499–1550","1515–1575":"1515–1575","1532–1627":"1532–1627","1469–1544":"1469–1544","1473–1560":"1473–1560","1473":"1473","1550":"1550","1495":"1495","1494":"1494","1560":"1560","Abt 1532":"noin 1532","1469":"1469","1544":"1544","1500":"1500","1532":"1532","1499":"1499","1575":"1575","1530":"1530","Abt 1495":"noin 1495","1627":"1627","1515":"1515","Stourton, Warwickshire, England":"Stourton, Warwickshire, England","Kent, England":"Kent, England","Whichford, Warwickshire, England":"Whichford, Warwickshire, England","Harrowden, Northamptonshire, England":"Harrowden, Northamptonshire, Eng